<h4 id="drive-guide---snowbird-mountain-from-i-40-west">Drive Guide - Snowbird Mountain from I-40 West</h4>

<ul>
  <li>R on Green Corner Rd and go 3.4</li>
  <li>L on Green Corner Rd and go 0.4</li>
  <li>R on Grassy Fork Rd and go 3.1  (turns to dirt at 1.3)
    <ul>
      <li>Too steep to drive to the top in 2WD.  Park in 90¬∞ pull-out on L at 35.7987,-83.0458.  (Room for 2 small cars.)  There are multiple spots where the road is so steep that 2WD spins its tires as gravel flows downhill, and the steepness doesn‚Äôt end until you reach the sharp turn just before the summit.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

