<h4 id="drive-guide---snowbird-mountain-to-atlanta">Drive Guide - Snowbird Mountain TO Atlanta</h4>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Duration</strong>: 3:45</li>
  <li><strong>Directions</strong>:
    <ul>
      <li>Head downhill on Grassy Fork Rd and go 4.2</li>
      <li>L on Green Corner Rd and go 3.8</li>
      <li>L onto I-40 East ramp and go 28</li>
      <li>Exit 27 to US-74 W and go 0.3</li>
      <li>US-74 W and go 25.6</li>
      <li>US-23 S / US-441 S and go 98</li>
      <li>I-985 S to I-85 S</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
